### Movies REST API — manual request collection
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension (or JetBrains HTTP client).
### Interactive docs: http://localhost:3000/docs

@host = http://localhost:3000

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Auth
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Register a new user (always created with role "user")
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login — returns a JWT in `token`. The seed admin can write movies.
# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin12345"
}

### Capture the token from the login response above for the protected routes.
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Movies — public reads
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List all movies
GET {{host}}/movies

### List with pagination, genre filter and sorting (-rate = descending)
GET {{host}}/movies?page=1&limit=5&genre=Action&sort=-rate

### Get a movie by id (replace with a real UUID)
GET {{host}}/movies/5ad1a235-0d9c-410a-b32b-220d91689a08

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Movies — protected writes (require an admin Bearer token)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create a movie
POST {{host}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Shrek",
  "year": 2001,
  "director": "Andrew Adamson",
  "duration": 90,
  "rate": 9,
  "poster": "https://example.com/shrek.jpg",
  "genre": ["Adventure", "Comedy"]
}

### Partially update a movie (PATCH — only send the fields you change)
PATCH {{host}}/movies/5ad1a235-0d9c-410a-b32b-220d91689a08
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rate": 9.1
}

### Delete a movie
DELETE {{host}}/movies/5ad1a235-0d9c-410a-b32b-220d91689a08
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# System
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
